flowchart TD
    A[Developer Writes<br/>Natural Language Requirements] --> B[Run qa_automation.py<br/>with --url or --data]
    B --> C[LangGraph Workflow<br/>Processes Request]
    C --> D[AI Generates Tests<br/>Based on Patterns & Prompts]
    D --> E[Test Files Created<br/>Cypress: cypress/e2e/<br/>Playwright: tests/]
    E --> F[Run Tests Locally<br/>npx cypress run<br/>or npx playwright test]
    F --> G{Tests Pass?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Commit & Push<br/>Ready for CI/CD]
    G -->|No| I[Debug & Analyze<br/>Use --analyze flag]
    I --> J[AI Provides Fixes<br/>Regenerate Tests]
    J --> F

    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style B fill:#fff3e0
    style C fill:#c8e6c9
    style D fill:#ffcdd2
